ctx: intros [isRing [commMult neutralMult]] integrity a x A_a A_x a_neq_O a_x.
exceptions.tactic: destruct (integrity a x) as [a_eq_O | x_eq_O]; [rewrite a_x in a_eq_O; contradiction | assumption].

original: intros [isRing [commMult neutralMult]] integrity a x A_a A_x a_neq_O a_x. destruct isRing as [commAdd [isGroupAdd [internMult [assocMult distrib]]]]. destruct (integrity a x) as [a_eq_O | x_eq_O]; [rewrite a_x in a_eq_O; contradiction | assumption].
